		<title>Apple to pay parents whose kids made unauthorized in-app purchases</title>
		<link>http://feeds.arstechnica.com/~r/arstechnica/everything/~3/whL7UqZHiqo/</link>
		<comments>http://arstechnica.com/apple/2013/06/apple-to-pay-parents-whose-kids-made-unauthorized-in-app-purchases/#comments</comments>
