		<title>Ellen Page thinks Naughty Dog “ripped off” her likeness for The Last of Us</title>
		<link>http://feeds.arstechnica.com/~r/arstechnica/everything/~3/HQEAkpq8DAg/</link>
		<comments>http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/06/ellen-page-thinks-naughty-dog-ripped-off-her-likeness-for-the-last-of-us/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2013 15:43:14 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Kyle Orland</dc:creator>
