		<title>Did Snowden’s travel plans hit a snag? Leaker fails to catch flight to Havana</title>
		<link>http://feeds.arstechnica.com/~r/arstechnica/everything/~3/hQeNkkXCBNg/</link>
		<comments>http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2013/06/did-snowdens-travel-plans-hit-a-snag-leaker-fails-to-catch-flight-to-havana/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2013 14:09:01 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Cyrus Farivar</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Law & Disorder]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Edward Snowden]]></category>
